---
title: Beef, Pork & Bacon Leek Bolognese Risotto with Parmesan & Balsamic Rocket Salad
description: If you thought bolognese and spaghetti were a match made in heaven, wait till you try it as a saucy risotto dish! Rice absorbs the
well-loved flavours of the bolognese in a way that pasta can’t - we think that this twist on a classic is a 10 out of 10.
